Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:47.34,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やり直せばいい 弱音吐くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夢にしがみつくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:59.27,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}願い　叶う日が来るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}川を渡れ! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.39,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不要為自己找藉口!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.10,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}沒試過又怎知道不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.61,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只能勇往直前!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不斷 一直 向前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.57,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一路拼命向前 穿過決定好的路途!
