Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.72,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}緊緊抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:59.27,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}直到夢想成真的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.69,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}橫渡激流! You can do it!
