Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.76,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不起眼的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:47.13,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是 不知為何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.88,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一直 很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:55.88,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}沒錯 不管在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:02.27,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你是最棒的
