Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.73,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}都無法與你相比
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:14.94,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你是最棒的
